data.description: Active Under Contract - Accepting back up offers...Cozy Country home on just over an acre lot.  The home features a newer roof (2017), 4 bedrooms, an office, a bonus room, screened front porch and large back screened lanai. When you walk into the home the open floorplan boasts a kitchen with large island overlooking  the living and dining room area. The Breakfast Nook features bay window with a storage seat. The large bonus room area offer could be used as a game room or additional living area. Wood appearance tile floors throughout the living room, kitchen, hallway and more. The oversized screened lanai overlooks the huge fenced in back yard. Beautiful vinyl fence.
